(51, 1, '2016-10-12 22:35:33', '2016-10-13 01:35:33', 'Each summer the City Government sectors enables beaches in the Children\'s Park and Rock THE PARK. These sectors have areas that are filled with sand where umbrellas, beach chairs and chairs to enjoy the outdoors are placed. There are also showers and games with water to cool. In addition there are public baths, parts of tables, children\'s games and wi-fi.\r\n\r\nLocation: Children\'s Park in the north of the city (+ see more) and the American Indian Park in the south.\r\nFrom January 8 to February 28, Tuesday to Sunday from 10 to 20 hours.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Children Park: General Paz and Avenida Cantilo (Colectora), Barrio Núñez + more</li>\r\n 	<li>American Indian Park: Avenida Castañares and Avenida Escalada, Villa Soldati</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHours: Tuesday to Sunday from 10 to 20 hours.', 'Buenos Aires Beach', 'Each summer the City Government sectors enables beaches in the Children\'s Park and Rock THE PARK. These sectors have areas that are filled with sand where umbrellas, beach chairs and chairs to enjoy the outdoors are placed. ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'buenos-aires-beach', '', '', '2016-10-12 22:35:54', '2016-10-13 01:35:54', '', 0, 'http://zola.dev/en/?p=51', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(52, 1, '2016-10-12 22:37:20', '2016-10-13 01:37:20', 'Summer is ideal for touring Buenos Aires and discover their neighborhoods and parks era. In addition there are different activities to perform.\r\n\r\nAs every year the city prepares to live the summer holidays 2017. During the summer season Buenos Aires offers different activities and places to visit.\r\n\r\nDuring the summer many city dwellers traveling for holidays and for that reason the pace of the city is more relaxed and quiet. The traffic is more agile and travel in public transport is more comfortable. Buenos Aires has many attractions and activities for the summer.\r\n\r\nTo note: During the summer the heat is intense and the temperature can exceed 30 ° degrees Celsius, for this reason it is recommended to stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water, use light clothing and avoid long walks in the sun.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://zola.dev/en/tigre-and-delta/">Tigre y Delta</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://zola.dev/en/parks-and-green-spaces/">Parques y espacios verdes</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://zola.dev/en/parque-norte-pools/">Piletas de Parque Norte</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Paseos culturales</li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://zola.dev/en/buenos-aires-beach/">Buenos Aires Playa</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Buenos Aires Summer', 'Summer is ideal for touring Buenos Aires and discover their neighborhoods and parks era. In addition there are different activities to perform.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'buenos-aires-summer', '', '', '2016-10-12 22:46:58', '2016-10-13 01:46:58', '', 0, 'http://zola.dev/en/?p=52', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(53, 1, '2016-10-12 22:42:12', '2016-10-13 01:42:12', 'The walk to Tiger is a classic summer. From the Tigre river station you can take collective to different recreations found on the Delta islands boats.\r\n\r\nRecesses are ideal for a day outdoors by the river. Recesses sectors have tables and grills, games, picnic areas, sports facilities and many have spas and beaches on rivers or streams. In the Tigre river station there are numerous offices and stalls offering a wide variety of recreations.', 'Tigre and Delta', 'The walk to Tiger is a classic summer. From the Tigre river station you can take collective to different recreations found on the Delta islands boats.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tigre-and-delta', '', '', '2016-10-12 22:42:12', '2016-10-13 01:42:12', '', 0, 'http://zola.dev/en/?p=53', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(54, 1, '2016-10-12 22:43:16', '2016-10-13 01:43:16', 'Buenos Aires parks are the preferred summer destinations in the city.\r\nThe most important are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bosques de Palermo / Rosedal</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque de los Niños</li>\r\n 	<li>Reserva Costanera Sur</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque Rivadavia</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque Avellaneda</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque Sarmiento</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque Saavedra</li>\r\n 	<li>Agronomía</li>\r\n 	<li>Parque Centenario</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Parks and green spaces', 'Buenos Aires parks are the preferred summer destinations in the city.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'parks-and-green-spaces', '', '', '2016-10-12 22:43:16', '2016-10-13 01:43:16', '', 0, 'http://zola.dev/en/?p=54', 0, 'post', '', 0),
